ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder Amending Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 278, Alberta
PrecisORDER AMENDING PROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 278 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of concern to the federal government; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to Alberta with respect to the interface fires that occurred in May 14 to August 18, 2024.
